{
  "stem": "22944.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my uncle-- we moved up there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Still all together?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Still all together-- for a little while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The caretaker was married to Maria.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had a daughter, Duli.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Helenka was the fiancee of William Gavalovic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her name was Helena Galova.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was working together with William in the mill, as a secretary, and she became his wife, eventually.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was very much involved with our rescue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She kept our morale up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Helenka and William, they used to come every single day after work to spend all the free time with us-- to humor us, to tell us the news, give us a little occupation.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they spent hours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, we were very, very fond of her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she was very, very young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she become like one of our family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we moved upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would like to tell you now the incident that happened previously was that Pernik said-- told me one day, when we were in hiding, around Christmas, I'm going to bring you a present.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was looking forward so much to the present.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He brought me his daughter, Duli, who was my age.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Duli, you must visualize it-- she was a kid of eight or nine year old, who was put in a big secret, to know there are Jews or people hiding, and a little girl of her own age.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As you can visualize, as any child would do, when they go back to school, would say, I know something-- you don't know something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But somehow they managed to put that it is sort of big secret.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Duli and I had very little to say first time that she came to visit me.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
